        { "lines": [
          { "filipino": "Ang aking kuya at ate ay parehong matalino.", "english": "My brother and sister are both intelligent.", "chinese": "我的哥哥和姊姊一樣聰明。", "pinyin": "Wǒ de gē gē hé jiě jiě yí yàng cōng míng." }
